padsof.gui.utils

Class GroupLayoutHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • padsof.gui.utils.GroupLayoutHelper

  • public class GroupLayoutHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper class to generate complex layouts using GroupLayout as a base. This class can be used with fluent syntax, with the static method fluidGenerateGroupLayout being the starting point.
    Author:
    Víctor de Juan Sanz - Guillermo Julián Moreno
